english.segment1: Verse 1: Lord I come before You. To honor and adore You. For who You are and all that You have done. Lord I am not worthy. My heart is dark and dirty. Still somehow You bid for me to come
english.segment2: Pre-Chorus: So clothe me in humility. Remind me, that I come before a King
english.segment3: Chorus: And there is nothing. There is nothing. More precious, more worthy. May I gaze deeper. May I stand longer. May I press onward to know You Lord
english.segment4: Verse 2: May our time be sweeter. May I be a keeper. Of the promises I make to You in song. Lord may I remember these moments of surrender. And live my life this way from this day on
